reviewText: Came on time and my sister loves it
This is a one time DVD to watch. Joyce Meyer is an inspirational speaker. This is a product recommended for those who are waiting on The Lord.

I purchased this dvd for my daughter because she is constantly saying, when God when?  Joyce Meyer has a way of
getting through to people because she speaks from experience and not from a textbook.  I would recommend this dvd
to anyone!
